				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Go to Jaheira's Basement with Jaheira\r\n- Straight ahead on the barrel, there's a semi-hidden scroll beneath a book and surrounded by rare alchemy items. Pick it up (Or read it) and Jaheira will talk to you about it\r\n\r\nBookmark: larian://bookmark?name=CTY_JaheiraBasement&mod=GustavDev&level=CTY_Main_A&camPos=-1537.007690;17.081484;1028.876221&camTarget=-1537.406860;16.317995;1028.368530"
